title: fool's speech
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

For up to 1 hour, up to 8 targets you choose within 30 feet of you gain the ability to speak a secret language. The language is incomprehensible to others and doesn't remotely sound like another [[language]]. Spells such as [[comprehend languages]] and [[tongues]] cannot decipher this language.